N
\f4\i0 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
= 462) seed cohorts. We used CERVUS (\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Marshall 
\f7\i \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
et al
\f4\i0 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
.  1998\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
) and GIMLET (Vali\'8fre 2002) to identify the mismatches and multiple-matches among endocarps and putative source trees. \
